        <div class="overview">

            <p><p><strong><span>Careers at Fecon</span></strong></p>
<p><span> </span></p>
<p><span>Fecon is a leading manufacturer in the Forestry and Construction Industries for track carriers and attachments. Our international headquarters is located in Lebanon, Ohio and is home of the Bull Hog® mulcher. Fecon is continually adding to and advancing our robust product line. In fact, we’ve recently added an additional 40,000 square feet of manufacturing space. There’s room for you to come and join this company on the move. </span></p>
<p><span>Fecon is always interested in speaking with skilled professionals. If a position you’re seeking is not posted and you are interested in working for Fecon, you’re welcome to forward your application or resume to our human resources department for future consideration.</span></p></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefits clear">
            <p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>
<p>Fecon offers an excellent, diverse work environment, competitive salaries, and employee benefit packages that include:</p>
<ul>
<li>         Medical Insurance</li>
<li>         Dental &amp; Vision Insurance</li>
<li>         Life Insurance</li>
<li>         401K Retirement Savings Plans</li>
<li>         Paid Vacation</li>
<li>         Paid Holidays</li>
<li>         Tuition Reimbursement</li>
</ul>
        </div>

        <div class=" clear"></div>
        </div>
    



