<li><span><span>    </span></span><span>Ability to work with customer and dealer personnel in a cooperative way to get a job or training mission accomplished.</span></li>
<li><span><span>    </span></span><span>Excellent people skills working with a diverse set of customers and dealers.</span></li>
<li><span><span>    </span></span><span>Skills to repair the customer as well as the equipment.</span></li>
<li><span><span>    </span></span><span>Willingness to see problems through to a satisfactory conclusion.</span></li>
<li><span><span>    </span></span><span>Good organizational and record-keeping skills are a must.</span></li>
